data.title: FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6
data.meta_description: The FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6 is a cutting-edge access control system combining facial and palm vein recognition. Featuring a sleek glass-aluminum design, FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6 boasts a 2MP binocular camera, a powerful 900 MHz dual-core CPU, and extensive memory for up to 1,000 face, 800 palm, and 1,000 card templates. Supporting RFID, MIFARE, and HID technologies, FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6 stores up to 150,000 transactions and offers various connectivity options like TCP/IP, USB, RS485, and optional WiFi. With a 4″ touchscreen, photo-ID capabilities, and access control features including lock relay output, alarms, and support for different sensors, FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6’s a versatile solution customizable to specific access needs.

data.text:
The FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6 is a cutting-edge access control system combining facial and palm vein recognition.

Featuring a sleek glass-aluminum design, FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6 boasts a 2MP binocular camera, a powerful 900 MHz dual-core CPU, and extensive memory for up to 1,000 face, 800 palm, and 1,000 card templates.

Supporting RFID, MIFARE, and HID technologies, FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6 stores up to 150,000 transactions and offers various connectivity options like TCP/IP, USB, RS485, and optional WiFi. With a 4″ touchscreen, photo-ID capabilities, and access control features including lock relay output, alarms, and support for different sensors, FingerTec AI Face Recognition Time Attendance & Door Access System Face ID 6’s a versatile solution customizable to specific access needs.
